{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC02_REG_090.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1b,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Thank you for the meal!<CR>Regina, the food was delicious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x49,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, I can only make simple things around here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Really? I thought it was really intricate."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x4b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Well, I've been cooking food for my<CR>family since I was a little girl,<CR>so I'm pretty good at cooking."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Now that I think about it, when I was young, you taught me how to cook..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x4c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Ooh, you're right. That was around the time I first moved out here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "You were so cute back then.<CR>Like, you were so bubbly!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Ever since then, you've always been taking care of me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "It was no prob, I like kids. And I had fun teaching you how to cook."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Regina, you're very domestic.<CR>I'm sure you'll make a great wife!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Right! I'm totally good at needlework, or any housework for that matter."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I mean, I'm from a big family, so I have time and experience to back me up!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Oh, is your family really that big?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Yup. Haven't I ever told you?<CR>I have five younger siblings."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "That many? Sounds like that would be so fun and lively."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I can't even imagine that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "It is lively. You have absolutely no time to be alone..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "If I let them be, my brothers would start fighting, and my sisters would start following me around."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Well, as their older sister,<CR>that's what makes them cute."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x11,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I'm working far from home, doing physical labor for those kids, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "If it's for them, no matter how tough it may get, I can keep on going."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Regina, you have a such a kind expression..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x169,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, am I acting out of character?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x16b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "But still, one of my younger brothers is gonna be all grown-up soon, so maybe I can start thinking about myself..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Oh, but my youngest brother is still<CR>pretty young...and my little sisters<CR>are a little unreliable."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I guess being the oldest sister is a lot of work..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, now that you got me started<CR>talking about them, I'm starting<CR>to miss my family now."
        }
    ]
}